com.spectralogic.ds3client.helpers

Interface JobPartTracker

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    JobPartTrackerImpl

    public interface JobPartTracker
    This class manages parts for all of the objects in the job. It aggregates ObjectPartTracker implementations, which manage the parts for a single object.
